General.Name: CAM Resources Bhd
General.Description: CAM Resources Berhad, an investment holding company, engages in the manufacture and trading of household products, palm oil milling, and renewable energy businesses. The company offers aluminum and stainless-steel kitchenware, kitchen sinks, and kitchen knives; plastic kitchenware; melamine tableware products; and plastic household products. It is also involved in processing and selling crude palm oil, oil palm fiber, palm kernel, and other related products. In addition, the company generates renewable energy; and acts as a transportation agent. It markets its aluminum and stainless household products under the Eagle and CAM brands; melamine tableware products under the Eagle brand name; and plastic kitchenware products under the KIWI, Goldenware, and Kiwiware brand names. The company operates in Malaysia, rest of Asia, the United States, and internationally. CAM Resources Berhad was incorporated in 2000 and is based in Hutan Melintang, Malaysia.
